 Mastodon 的 Troy Sanders 被评为年度地区少年联盟教练：“没有什么比这更让我喜欢的了” https://www.nme.com/news/music/mastodons-troy-sanders-named-regional-little-league-coach-of-the-year-theres-nothing-i-love-more-3608953?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=mastodons-troy-sanders-named-regional-little-league-the-year-theres-nothing-i-love-moreHollie Geraghty Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:16:10 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3608953 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乳齿象的特洛伊·桑德斯" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位音乐家表示，他对得到认可感到“非常兴奋和谦卑”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mastodons-troy-sanders-named-regional-little-league-coach-of-the-year-theres-nothing-i-love-more-3608953">Mastodon 队的特洛伊·桑德斯 (Troy Sanders) 被评为年度地区少年棒球联盟教练：“没有什么比我更喜欢的了”，这句话</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="乳齿象的特洛伊·桑德斯" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/troy-sanders-mastodon-little-league-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mastadon">Mastodon</a>的 Troy Sanders 被评为年度地区棒球教练，以表彰他在少年棒球联盟中的工作。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：乳齿象： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mastodon-hushed-and-grim-interview-brann-dailor-3087709">“我们不会互相谈论我们的感受，我们只是把它们写在歌词中”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位贝斯手兼歌手在他儿子所在的佛罗里达州少年棒球联盟帮忙，担任联盟主席、教练和裁判。</p><p>这位美国重金属音乐家<a href="https://www.littleleague.org/news/florida-little-league-coach-named-positive-coaching-alliances-regional-baseball-coach-of-the-year/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">早在 1 月份就</a>被积极教练联盟 (Positive Coaching Alliance) 评为 2024 年度地区棒球教练，本月<a href="https://www.metalsucks.net/2024/03/11/mastodons-troy-sanders-is-a-damn-good-little-league-coach/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MetalSucks</a>也将这一奖项授予了他。</p><p>桑德斯和其他 35 名地区获奖者是从全国 500 多名提名教练中选出的。</p><p>桑德斯在<a href="https://www.littleleague.org/news/florida-little-league-coach-named-positive-coaching-alliances-regional-baseball-coach-of-the-year/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">少年棒球联盟的一篇新闻文章</a>中说：“我没有预料到这一点，也对此一无所知，直到我收到通知我被选中的电子邮件。” “然后，当我做了更多研究并了解了 10 名现任和前任球员的父母为我经历的提名流程后，我感到非常兴奋和谦卑。”</p><p>他补充道：“以我认为最自然的方式来执教和领导这些在我自己的圈子之外得到认可的年轻球员，这让我觉得我至少在为这些孩子做一些正确的事情，而且能够成为这些球员让我感到很兴奋。”就这样被认可了。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2khe0cO6_Q/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.